---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Australian Home Collective and its practical home guides for Australian households."
>
  <header class="page-intro">
    <div class="narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>About Australian Home Collective</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Australian Home Collective is a practical home guide site for Australian households.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="content narrow">
    <p>
      The site focuses on everyday product types, storage ideas, home setup decisions and
      useful buying considerations across kitchens, laundries, bedrooms, bathrooms, pets,
      nurseries, living spaces, home offices, garages and outdoor areas.
    </p>
    <p>
      Australian Home Collective was created to make home product research feel less
      overwhelming. The site focuses on practical product types, storage ideas, and everyday
      buying considerations for Australian households.
    </p>
    <p>
      The aim is simple: help readers work out what they actually need before comparing
      products, brands, or retailers.
    </p>

    <h2>What we focus on</h2>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>Practical product types.</li>
      <li>Storage and organisation.</li>
      <li>Everyday home setup.</li>
      <li>Australian conditions and household needs.</li>
      <li>Clear, useful guidance without fake testing claims.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What we do not do</h2>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>We do not claim hands-on product testing unless clearly stated.</li>
      <li>We do not present paid placement as independent advice.</li>
      <li>We do not include exact prices unless they can be checked and kept current.</li>
      <li>We do not recommend products based only on hype.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      You can also read more about <a href="/how-we-select-products/">how we choose what to include</a>.
    </p>
    <p class="small">
      Images and written content on this site are owned by Australian Home Collective unless
      otherwise stated.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
